dct_title_s: Plan de la ville de Dakar en 1862
dct_description_sm: Scale 1:10,000 ; Map originally folded ; Relief shown by form lines ; Includes index with locations of buildings and other features ; 'Projet de Mr. le gouverneur Pinet-Laprade' ; Paris : E. Larose
